1
00:00:05,585 --> 00:00:08,281
<i>Press down hard on the gas</i>

2
00:00:08,355 --> 00:00:12,223
<i>That's right, there's no compromise</i>

3
00:00:12,292 --> 00:00:16,285
<i>We'll slip through the night</i>

4
00:00:16,630 --> 00:00:19,121
<i>At the final moment push hard</i>

5
00:00:19,199 --> 00:00:23,260
<i>That's right, all the way to zero,</i>

6
00:00:23,336 --> 00:00:27,295
<i>Until we wipe away the days</i>

7
00:00:28,775 --> 00:00:33,508
<i>Gently open your heart</i>

8
00:00:34,214 --> 00:00:37,183
<i>If you pull it close to you</i>

9
00:00:39,619 --> 00:00:41,712
<i>It will reach you, without a doubt</i>

10
00:00:42,456 --> 00:00:43,753
<i>It will come, closer</i>

11
00:00:44,091 --> 00:00:46,651
<i>Now</i>

12
00:00:54,701 --> 00:01:00,071
<i>We're speeding through life,</i>
<i>squeezing it for all of its worth</i>

13
00:01:00,273 --> 00:01:01,433
<i>Our feet are tied</i>

14
00:01:01,508 --> 00:01:05,308
<i>But we still keep going farther</i>

15
00:01:05,645 --> 00:01:10,844
<i>Even if I take it back, and grasp it</i>

16
00:01:11,118 --> 00:01:12,449
<i>If you're not the one</i>

17
00:01:12,519 --> 00:01:13,918
<i>There will be no meaning</i>

18
00:01:13,987 --> 00:01:20,256
<i>And so we'll go far off into the distance.</i>

19
00:01:33,985 --> 00:01:35,816
If there's an instance that we
become separated,

20
00:01:36,521 --> 00:01:38,682
don't trust him if he looks
like your teammate.

21
00:01:39,957 --> 00:01:42,084
Just like now there's a possibility

22
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:43,650
that an enemy will transform
to get close to us!

23
00:01:44,162 --> 00:01:44,856
Yeah.

24
00:01:44,929 --> 00:01:46,328
So what do we do?

25
00:01:47,431 --> 00:01:49,058
We'll decide on a password.

26
00:01:49,467 --> 00:01:51,367
Password?

27
00:01:52,436 --> 00:01:55,166
I'll only say it once so listen closely.

28
00:01:56,541 --> 00:01:58,065
You ask Ninja song, "Ninja Chance."

29
00:01:58,342 --> 00:02:00,367
And the answer is this:

30
00:02:01,579 --> 00:02:03,843
"It is a chance to sneak up where a large
number of enemies are making a scene.

31
00:02:04,148 --> 00:02:06,514
"The quiet place has
no secret hideout.

32
00:02:07,852 --> 00:02:10,878
"It is important for
a Shinobi to know the right time.

33
00:02:11,355 --> 00:02:13,823
"The time when an enemy
is tired and drops his guard."

34
00:02:14,292 --> 00:02:15,020
That's it.

35
00:02:16,160 --> 00:02:17,491
H-Huge!

36
00:02:21,833 --> 00:02:22,697
T-Tail!

37
00:02:29,140 --> 00:02:32,166
You want our Earth Scroll, don't you?

38
00:02:45,756 --> 00:02:48,190
Well, let's begin...

39
00:02:50,761 --> 00:02:53,161
the battle for the Scrolls.

40
00:02:56,133 --> 00:02:57,498
Life or death!

41
00:03:06,744 --> 00:03:09,304
<i>If this creature doesn't want</i>
<i>to spit me out...</i>

42
00:03:10,114 --> 00:03:13,049
<i>I'll make it to do so at any cost!</i>

43
00:03:15,286 --> 00:03:17,049
Shadow Clone Jutsu!

44
00:03:24,362 --> 00:03:25,329
<i>I can't move!</i>

45
00:03:29,433 --> 00:03:32,197
I wanted you to entertain me more.

46
00:03:33,971 --> 00:03:35,029
It's too bad.

47
00:03:40,544 --> 00:03:41,636
Move!

48
00:03:47,785 --> 00:03:50,276
<i>He wiped out the fear with pain.</i>

49
00:03:53,224 --> 00:03:56,455
<i>As expected,</i>
<i>he's not the average prey.</i>

50
00:04:05,636 --> 00:04:06,967
Don't come near me!

51
00:04:14,578 --> 00:04:17,445
Don't lower your guard,
not even for a moment...

52
00:04:27,959 --> 00:04:33,329
A prey must always stay tense
and flee desperately

53
00:04:35,166 --> 00:04:37,259
before a predator!

54
00:04:49,046 --> 00:04:50,673
Sorry Sasuke.

55
00:04:58,155 --> 00:04:59,122
Naruto!

56
00:05:01,625 --> 00:05:05,527
The password... I forgot it!

57
00:05:06,497 --> 00:05:11,799
<i>Naruto's Counterattack.</i>
<i>Never Give In!</i>

58
00:05:18,609 --> 00:05:22,807
The password... I forgot it!

59
00:05:23,781 --> 00:05:25,043
That's all right, Naruto!

60
00:05:25,249 --> 00:05:26,273
Awesome!

61
00:05:29,987 --> 00:05:30,851
Naruto!

62
00:05:31,122 --> 00:05:33,317
I know you tried to be cool and
intended to rescue us, but...

63
00:05:33,391 --> 00:05:34,380
Don't put your nose in this!

64
00:05:34,625 --> 00:05:35,421
Escape!

65
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:38,885
This thing...
She's on a far different level!

66
00:05:38,963 --> 00:05:43,696
Seems like you brought that
giant snake down brilliantly, Naruto.

67
00:05:45,069 --> 00:05:49,403
<i>No matter how you look,</i>
<i>she looks like a snake...</i>

68
00:05:55,246 --> 00:05:58,682
<i>I get it, it was the handiwork</i>
<i>of this woman.</i>

69
00:06:04,955 --> 00:06:08,516
<i>The situation has never gotten any better</i>
<i>with him showing up for the rescue.</i>

70
00:06:09,960 --> 00:06:11,325
<i>But what should I do?</i>

71
00:06:11,395 --> 00:06:17,197
Hey hey hey! Evidently you've been
bullying the weakling!

72
00:06:17,635 --> 00:06:20,263
Now that I, Naruto Uzumaki is here,

73
00:06:20,337 --> 00:06:22,396
I'm going to wipe the floor with you!

74
00:06:22,506 --> 00:06:26,408
<i>Damn it! If it continues like this,</i>
<i>all three of us are done for!</i>

75
00:06:28,279 --> 00:06:29,337
<i>What should I do?</i>

76
00:06:36,287 --> 00:06:37,845
<i>Sasuke...</i>

77
00:06:46,130 --> 00:06:47,154
<i>It's no good.</i>

78
00:06:49,033 --> 00:06:50,364
<i>This is the only way.</i>

79
00:06:54,705 --> 00:06:55,569
Wait.

80
00:06:55,906 --> 00:06:56,668
Hmm?

81
00:06:56,907 --> 00:06:58,306
- Huh?!
- Huh?

82
00:07:05,116 --> 00:07:07,641
If it's the scroll you want,
I'll give it to you.

83
00:07:08,319 --> 00:07:11,516
I'm asking you.
Just take this and go.

84
00:07:11,689 --> 00:07:13,054
Huh?!

85
00:07:13,491 --> 00:07:14,423
What?!

86
00:07:16,760 --> 00:07:19,820
Hey, Sasuke!
What are you doing?

87
00:07:19,897 --> 00:07:22,559
Why are you giving
our scroll to the enemy?

88
00:07:22,867 --> 00:07:24,391
You, shut up!

89
00:07:24,668 --> 00:07:25,726
What?!

90
00:07:26,637 --> 00:07:29,765
I see...
You're sensible.

91
00:07:32,877 --> 00:07:35,641
The only thing the "prey" can
hope for from the "predator" is

92
00:07:36,013 --> 00:07:41,246
presenting other food and
pray you would be spared, isn't it?

93
00:07:51,195 --> 00:07:52,389
Take it.

94
00:07:52,563 --> 00:07:53,530
Wha?!

95
00:08:01,505 --> 00:08:03,473
You! Don't interfere with this!

96
00:08:03,908 --> 00:08:05,569
Don't you understand this situation?!

97
00:08:14,852 --> 00:08:17,616
What're you doing all of a sudden?!

98
00:08:30,868 --> 00:08:34,463
As for me,
I don't remember the password...

99
00:08:34,939 --> 00:08:37,669
So I got no way to make sure.

100
00:08:38,242 --> 00:08:41,143
But you, you're an imposter
Sasuke, aren't you?

101
00:08:41,312 --> 00:08:42,244
Naruto!

102
00:08:42,413 --> 00:08:45,041
W-What are you trying to start?!

103
00:08:45,816 --> 00:08:49,513
You loser!
I'm the real me!

104
00:08:51,855 --> 00:08:52,913
Liar.

105
00:08:54,959 --> 00:09:04,061
This, this stupid coward is... absolutely...
not the Sasuke I know!

106
00:09:04,935 --> 00:09:07,369
I don't know how strong she is but,

107
00:09:07,438 --> 00:09:12,535
how can you be sure that she'll let us
go if we hand over the Scroll, huh?!

108
00:09:14,411 --> 00:09:19,178
You're the one who choked and
doesn't understand this situation!

109
00:09:22,152 --> 00:09:23,312
Naruto.

110
00:09:26,857 --> 00:09:28,188
That's correct.

111
00:09:31,528 --> 00:09:32,688
The Scroll.

112
00:09:36,333 --> 00:09:39,393
I could just kill you
and seize it.

113
00:09:44,174 --> 00:09:45,573
Don't mess with me!

114
00:09:45,643 --> 00:09:47,440
Run, Naruto! Stop it!

115
00:09:47,978 --> 00:09:49,309
<i>Damn it!</i>

116
00:09:50,314 --> 00:09:52,214
<i>I've lost confidence in you, Sasuke!</i>

117
00:09:52,716 --> 00:09:53,944
Summoning Jutsu!

118
00:10:06,330 --> 00:10:07,194
Naruto!

119
00:10:22,046 --> 00:10:23,479
There are three corpses.

120
00:10:24,915 --> 00:10:28,078
This is some kind of Ninja Art,
isn't it?

121
00:10:28,752 --> 00:10:31,448
This is bad.

122
00:10:35,225 --> 00:10:37,625
We have a problem,
from the get go.

123
00:10:38,329 --> 00:10:39,296
I'll be damned.

124
00:10:45,636 --> 00:10:48,537
Inform Anko,
the Proctor of the second test.

125
00:10:48,672 --> 00:10:49,400
Yes, sir!

126
00:10:54,878 --> 00:10:58,575
If you're going to have dumplings,
you've got to have sweet red bean soup.

127
00:11:01,885 --> 00:11:05,412
Okay...
Once I've eaten this,

128
00:11:05,522 --> 00:11:09,049
I should break through and
go wait at the tower for the kids.

129
00:11:10,694 --> 00:11:15,688
With this program, the quick kids
should clear it soon.

130
00:11:17,267 --> 00:11:19,167
The Leaf Village mark, perfect!

131
00:11:24,908 --> 00:11:26,603
We have a problem, Ms. Anko!

132
00:11:27,411 --> 00:11:30,005
Huh? What, so suddenly?

133
00:11:30,414 --> 00:11:31,938
Corpses! Three of them!

134
00:11:35,452 --> 00:11:36,510
Moreover, they're strange.

135
00:11:36,987 --> 00:11:38,614
Anyway, please come!

136
00:11:41,525 --> 00:11:42,583
Strange?

137
00:11:50,567 --> 00:11:53,195
I checked their possessions
and identification,

138
00:11:53,804 --> 00:11:58,707
Ninjas from Grass Village
registered in the Chunin Exam, but...

139
00:11:59,643 --> 00:12:00,905
As you can see...

140
00:12:04,047 --> 00:12:05,605
They have no faces.

141
00:12:08,018 --> 00:12:08,916
Yes.

142
00:12:10,053 --> 00:12:13,682
They're smooth and flat,
like they melted away.

143
00:12:18,128 --> 00:12:19,493
<i>Without a doubt...</i>

144
00:12:20,397 --> 00:12:21,728
<i>This Jutsu is...</i>

145
00:12:24,368 --> 00:12:25,562
<i>that man's...</i>

146
00:12:27,204 --> 00:12:29,104
<i>Why is he at this test?</i>

147
00:12:53,521 --> 00:12:56,354
Show me the ID photos of
these three Grass Village Ninjas.

148
00:12:56,591 --> 00:12:57,853
It's on their applications.

149
00:12:57,926 --> 00:12:58,950
Yes!

150
00:13:01,997 --> 00:13:03,464
<i>So this one's face was robbed.</i>

151
00:13:06,201 --> 00:13:08,226
<i>Then, at that time it was already...</i>

152
00:13:10,372 --> 00:13:12,840
<i>I'll return... the Kunai knife.</i>

153
00:13:13,541 --> 00:13:15,236
<i>Thank you for your trouble.</i>

154
00:13:19,948 --> 00:13:21,279
We're in big trouble.

155
00:13:21,449 --> 00:13:22,177
Huh?!

156
00:13:22,584 --> 00:13:25,883
Communicate this to
Lord Hokage right away!

157
00:13:26,554 --> 00:13:29,045
Make a call for action to
the Anbu Black Ops

158
00:13:29,124 --> 00:13:31,024
to assemble more than two squads
to the Forest of Death!

159
00:13:31,826 --> 00:13:34,158
Starting now,
I'm going to follow these guys!

160
00:13:34,229 --> 00:13:35,025
Got it?

161
00:13:35,096 --> 00:13:35,790
Yes!

162
00:13:40,435 --> 00:13:41,163
<i>That guy...</i>

163
00:13:41,970 --> 00:13:44,200
<i>That guy... has come to Leaf Village!</i>

164
00:13:58,586 --> 00:13:59,780
Cute.

165
00:14:00,588 --> 00:14:02,886
You're such a cute prey.

166
00:14:08,296 --> 00:14:09,024
Naruto!

167
00:14:09,464 --> 00:14:10,556
Narutooo!

168
00:14:19,974 --> 00:14:22,374
Well, polish him off.

169
00:14:39,160 --> 00:14:40,821
Shove it!

170
00:14:52,073 --> 00:14:53,938
This brat! Can't be...

171
00:15:03,284 --> 00:15:05,650
Naruto... He's lost control...

172
00:15:06,087 --> 00:15:09,921
But... that Naruto,
why is he so strong?!

173
00:15:31,513 --> 00:15:32,605
Those eyes...

174
00:15:32,781 --> 00:15:34,214
There's no mistake.

175
00:15:35,250 --> 00:15:37,844
That's... Naruto?!

176
00:15:39,788 --> 00:15:41,517
<i>This just got interesting.</i>

177
00:15:43,024 --> 00:15:43,888
Next is...

178
00:15:46,494 --> 00:15:47,552
Sasuke.

179
00:15:48,029 --> 00:15:49,553
Now what's your move?!

180
00:15:57,038 --> 00:15:57,936
Sasuke!

181
00:16:09,918 --> 00:16:10,907
<i>I have to hurry.</i>

182
00:16:13,288 --> 00:16:14,277
<i>I get this...</i>

183
00:16:16,191 --> 00:16:17,419
<i>bad feeling.</i>

184
00:16:36,611 --> 00:16:40,172
Hey. Are you hurt?

185
00:16:46,087 --> 00:16:47,577
Scaredy cat?!

186
00:16:56,664 --> 00:16:57,528
<i>Naruto!</i>

187
00:16:59,467 --> 00:17:00,058
<i>Hey!</i>

188
00:17:01,669 --> 00:17:03,193
<i>Are you hurt...</i>

189
00:17:04,873 --> 00:17:06,101
<i>Scaredy cat?</i>

190
00:17:10,144 --> 00:17:11,475
<i>Sasuke!</i>

191
00:17:16,017 --> 00:17:22,081
This stupid coward is absolutely
not the Sasuke I know!

192
00:17:29,330 --> 00:17:30,160
Huh?!

193
00:17:31,733 --> 00:17:35,692
Damn it!
Let me go!

194
00:17:35,970 --> 00:17:37,301
You stupid snake!

195
00:17:40,041 --> 00:17:44,307
<i>To think that the</i>
<i>nine tailed brat lived...</i>

196
00:17:48,249 --> 00:17:52,948
<i>When you get excited, a bit</i>
<i>of the nine tail's power trickles out...</i>

197
00:17:58,426 --> 00:18:00,986
<i>You've grown up interesting.</i>

198
00:18:04,332 --> 00:18:05,162
<i>Look...</i>

199
00:18:05,667 --> 00:18:07,931
<i>The Seal is appearing on</i>
<i>your skin like a tattoo.</i>

200
00:18:12,340 --> 00:18:15,070
Five-Pronged... Sealing

201
00:18:26,854 --> 00:18:28,788
Sasuke! Help Naruto!

202
00:18:39,701 --> 00:18:41,498
<i>Twelve years since the seal...</i>

203
00:18:41,970 --> 00:18:47,101
<i>Naruto's Chakras and the nine tail's</i>
<i>Chakras are beginning to act in synch...</i>

204
00:18:52,313 --> 00:18:55,840
<i>But now... you're in the way.</i>

205
00:19:01,456 --> 00:19:03,424
<i>He's gonna fall as it is!</i>

206
00:19:03,992 --> 00:19:05,050
Naruto!

207
00:19:08,696 --> 00:19:10,220
What happened Sasuke?!

208
00:19:14,669 --> 00:19:15,658
<i>Sasuke...</i>

209
00:19:22,343 --> 00:19:25,710
Naruto's certainly different
from you, Sasuke.

210
00:19:25,980 --> 00:19:28,471
He's a klutz and
kind of gets in the way.

211
00:19:29,050 --> 00:19:31,883
But he's not in the least a coward!

212
00:19:32,420 --> 00:19:34,411
Right?
Isn't that right?

213
00:19:42,163 --> 00:19:44,256
<i>You foolish little brother.</i>

214
00:19:45,066 --> 00:19:49,765
<i>If you want to kill me,</i>
<i>resent me, hate me and...</i>

215
00:19:50,405 --> 00:19:53,704
<i>continue to live your ugly life.</i>

216
00:19:54,609 --> 00:19:55,405
<i>Flee.</i>

217
00:19:55,643 --> 00:19:59,636
<i>Flee and hang on to your life.</i>

218
00:20:02,550 --> 00:20:03,812
<i>No!</i>

219
00:20:12,994 --> 00:20:18,364
<i>Just what I expect of the Uchiha clan...</i>
<i>his blood has begun to stir...</i>

220
00:20:22,437 --> 00:20:23,369
Sasuke!

221
00:20:27,442 --> 00:20:31,344
<i>I should take my time and</i>
<i>confirm his true power.</i>

222
00:21:05,436 --> 00:21:10,032
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

223
00:21:10,140 --> 00:21:18,240
<i>The clear, blue sky goes on and on</i>

224
00:21:19,316 --> 00:21:27,849
<i>The ocean spans limitlessly</i>

225
00:21:28,459 --> 00:21:36,161
<i>Please keep that smile on your face forever</i>

226
00:21:37,568 --> 00:21:43,097
<i>Or else I'll cry</i>

227
00:21:43,173 --> 00:21:46,939
<i>You won't have to search around you</i>

228
00:21:47,010 --> 00:21:50,571
<i>It's all ok now.</i>

229
00:21:51,048 --> 00:21:59,456
<i>Everyone is inside</i>
<i>this hand</i>

230
00:21:59,857 --> 00:22:04,920
<i>when you want to cry, and you want to run away</i>

231
00:22:04,995 --> 00:22:09,398
<i>When you forget what happiness is</i>

232
00:22:09,566 --> 00:22:13,229
<i>Just sing.</i>

233
00:22:13,537 --> 00:22:18,634
<i>Light is born, and darkness was born</i>

234
00:22:18,776 --> 00:22:20,903
<i>The two are one</i>

235
00:22:21,011 --> 00:22:27,280
<i>Harmonia, feel the telepathy</i>

236
00:22:27,885 --> 00:22:32,879
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

237
00:22:37,794 --> 00:22:38,988
I'm an avenger.

238
00:22:39,596 --> 00:22:42,690
To defeat my brother,
today I have to survive!

239
00:22:43,666 --> 00:22:47,261
But how can a person who won't risk
his life in a situation like this

240
00:22:47,337 --> 00:22:49,168
beat my brother?

241
00:22:50,373 --> 00:22:52,307
Calm down, you should be able to see.

242
00:22:52,742 --> 00:22:54,801
There should be some way
to intercept her movements.

243
00:22:56,346 --> 00:23:00,544
Next episode: "The Sharingan Revived:
Dragon-Flame Jutsu!"
